text: Hemipristis plicatilis is an extinct species of wealsel sharks that lived in Cretaceous period. The species was been describried by Kiprijanoff V. in 1854. == References == Category:Cretaceous Category:Animals of Russia Category:Hemipristis Category:Hemigalidae Category:Carcharhiniformes Category:Extinct fish Category:Sharks
title: Hemipristis plicatilis
